text.tspan: To support fve city-regions along the continuum of ecological
sustainability and economic growth with a strong focus on equity. We
aim to develop empirically driven spatial and statistical analysis,
create multi-stakeholder forums for dialogue and collaborative action,
strengthen local capacity and capability and empower local
stakeholders to be change makers through our technical support.
